message: This computer gets slow and the fan starts turning, I ran asd os and the following error appears TC0D CPU 0 Die analog, any suggestions

CPU die temperature sensor is embedded into CPU.
You can check U5510 solders and traces for pins 2 & 3.

Run HWMonitor and check all temps reported.

Just in case, remove/replace C5511.

I don't see bad solders u5510, nor bad traces pin 2 and pin 3, replace c5511 persist problem this hwmonitor

[ATTACH type="full"]61258[/ATTACH]

The problem may be CPU itself.

Just in case, change U5510...
